42 (4) For the purposes of this subsection, the Chatham County legislative delegation shall
43 be composed of all senators and representatives in the General Assembly whose districts
44 are wholly or partially in Chatham County."
45 "(h) A quorum of the authority shall be a majority of the board members authorized by this
46 Act. No vacancy on the authority shall impair the right of the quorum to exercise all of the
47 rights and perform all the duties of the authority."
48 SECTION 2.
49 This Act shall become effective on July 1, 2025.
50 SECTION 3.
51 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
